                     <interp inst="t18340102-25-verdict143" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 37. - Recommended to mercy by Jury believing it to be his first offence - <rs id="t18340102-25-punish144" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340102-25-punish144" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340102-25-defend275 t18340102-25-punish144"></join>
               Confined Eighteen Months
            </rs>.</p>
